<!-- FAQ for Contact -->
<section class="section animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Booking Information</h2>
            <p>Important details about booking and preparation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two-column">
            <div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How far in advance should I book?</h4>
                    <p>We recommend booking 4-6 weeks in advance, especially for weddings and popular dates. However, we can often accommodate last-minute requests if available.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What information do you need to provide a quote?</h4>
                    <p>Event date, location, type of event, expected guest count, and preferred service duration. The more details you provide, the more accurate our quote will be.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Do you require a deposit?</h4>
                    <p>Yes, we require a 50% deposit to secure your date. The remaining balance is due on the day of your event. We accept cash, check, and all major credit cards.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What happens if it rains (outdoor events)?</h4>
                    <p>We can adapt to covered outdoor areas or move indoors if needed. Our equipment is weather-resistant, and we'll work with you to ensure your event goes smoothly.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How much space do you need?</h4>
                    <p>We need approximately 8x8 feet of space for the photobooth setup, plus additional space for guests to pose and move around comfortably.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Do you provide liability insurance?</h4>
                    <p>Yes, we carry comprehensive liability insurance. We can provide certificates of insurance for venues that require it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

